        <Param val="Welcome to join the experiment.&amp;#10;First you will see 2 color and 2 audio in the studying phase. Try to memorize it. During the second stage, you need to make decision if the color and audio match previous stage. Press [Yes] or [No] to make response. &amp;#10;Now, we will start practice block. Press [Space] to continue." valType="str" updates="constant" name="text"/>
